The paper proposes a method for image caption generation, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The method involves attention mechanisms and fine-tuning of neural networks, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions evaluation metrics such as BLEU, METEOR, and CIDEr, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR).
